  "commit_message": "checks/code_integrity: fix ty invalid-assignment in uefi detection\n\nlist(raw_known) where raw_known is inferred as list[object] (YAML-parsed\ndict value) produces list[object], which ty correctly rejects as not\nassignable to list[str]. Replace with a comprehension that filters to\nstr instances - the correct semantics for YAML-parsed key names anyway,\nsince YAML will always emit strings for this config field.\n\nSigned-off-by: Javier Tia <floss@jetm.me>",
